    </item>
    <item>
      <title>塔塔钢铁公司将在多年亏损后关闭英国高炉</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-19/tata-steel-shares-jump-on-reports-of-closure-of-uk-furnaces</link>
      <description><![CDATA[塔塔钢铁有限公司计划关闭英国塔尔伯特港的两座亏损高炉，此前该公司已获得政府融资，将这座历史悠久的遗址改造成再生钢生产中心。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-19/tata-steel-shares-jump-on-reports-of-closure-of-uk-furnaces</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Jan 2024 06:54:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>能源成本上升拖累产量，巴斯夫盈利大幅下滑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-19/basf-earnings-crater-as-lower-margins-outweigh-cost-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴斯夫公司去年的盈利大幅下滑，原因是能源支出飙升抵消了成本削减，并对这家欧洲最大化学品公司的生产造成了压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-19/basf-earnings-crater-as-lower-margins-outweigh-cost-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Jan 2024 06:32:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
